      "Supporting": "Peripheral eosinophilia and systemic neurological involvement.",
      "Against": "Patient lacks history of asthma or sinus disease; onset is acute rather than chronic; CSF findings strongly point toward an infectious etiology.",
      "Support_Level": "Weakly supported"
    },
